運輸之舟、\r\n    車、航空機內而犯之。\r\n前項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e6%98%93%2c207%2c20220330%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,易,207,20220330,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"易","JNO":"207","JDATE":"20220330","JTITLE":"加重竊盜"}